with Lazarus...</i>

16
00:01:59.623 --> 00:02:04.294
- Pick up that hammer. boy.
- Yes. sir. boss.

17
00:02:04.544 --> 00:02:08.048
<i>Well. he's a dangerous man</i>

18
00:02:08.381 --> 00:02:15.388
<i>O Lord. he's a dangerous man...</i>

19
