548
00:37:08.773 --> 00:37:11.818
Now. what do you suppose
is eatin' George?

549
00:37:12.068 --> 00:37:16.740
Well. they say that with
the thrill-seeking personality.

550
00:37:17.073 --> 00:37:18.700
what goes up must come down.

551
00:37:18.950 --> 00:37:22.162
Top of the world one minute.
sad the next.

552
00:37:22.496 --> 00:37:27.042
Yes. sir. it's as if
our old friend George is a alley cat

553
00:37:27.292 --> 00:37:30.253
