are swingin' him by the tail.

554
00:37:30.504 --> 00:37:34.257
I wouldn't worry. Delmar.
He'll be back on top again.

555
00:37:34.424 --> 00:37:40.180
I don't think we've seen
the last of George Nelson.

556
00:37:58.114 --> 00:38:01.117
<i>Don't be saps for Pappy.</i>

557
00:38:01.451 --> 00:38:03.787
<i>Homer Stokes for governor.</i>

558
00:38:03.954 --> 00:38:08.542
