No!

1218
01:27:15.655 --> 01:27:18.158
<i>Is you is. or is you ain't
my constituency?</i>

1219
01:27:18.408 --> 01:27:20.494
No!

1220
01:27:20.660 --> 01:27:23.246
Is you is...

1221
01:27:23.622 --> 01:27:28.001
Is you is.
or is you ain't my constituency?

1222
01:27:28.168 --> 01:27:30.670
