1227
01:28:02.869 --> 01:28:07.290
<i>It's fair to tell</i>

1228
01:28:07.457 --> 01:28:10.085
<i>My only lover</i>

1229
01:28:10.293 --> 01:28:12.671
<i>I never expect</i>

1230
01:28:13.046 --> 01:28:16.550
<i>To see you again</i>

1231
01:28:16.967 --> 01:28:21.221
<i>For I'm bound to ride</i>

1232
01:28:21.471 --> 01:28:24.141
<i>That northern railroad</i>

1233
01:28:24.391 --> 01:28:29.312
<i>Perhaps I'll die upon that train</i>

1234
