God damn!
Opportunity knocks!

1236
01:28:39.072 --> 01:28:41.366
Get out of my way!

1237
01:28:41.658 --> 01:28:44.161
<i>I'm just a stranger</i>

1238
01:28:44.411 --> 01:28:47.038
<i>In case you ever</i>

1239
