<i>I'll meet you on</i>

1243
01:29:01.094 --> 01:29:03.722
<i>God's golden shore</i>

1244
01:29:04.014 --> 01:29:06.600
<i>He'll meet you on</i>

1245
01:29:06.892 --> 01:29:09.519
<i>God's golden shore</i>

1246
