- No wedding.

1307
01:32:38.311 --> 01:32:39.729
We'll fetch it with you.

1308
01:32:39.980 --> 01:32:42.899
It's just... Shut up. Delmar.
It's just a symbol.

1309
01:32:43.066 --> 01:32:46.653
I've spoken my piece
and counted to three.

1310
01:32:46.820 --> 01:32:50.574
She counted to three. God damn it.

1311
01:32:50.907 --> 01:32:53.743
She counted to three. Son of a bitch!

1312
01:32:53.994 --> 01:32:56.496
You have any idea
how far that cabin is?

1313
