Please. Lord.

1362
01:36:49.896 --> 01:36:53.650
I just want to see
my daughters again.

1363
01:36:53.984 --> 01:36:57.904
I've been separated
from my family for so long.

1364
01:36:58.155 --> 01:37:01.491
I know I've been guilty of pride
and sharp dealing.

1365
01:37:01.658 --> 01:37:03.994
I'm sorry I turned my back on you.

1366
