<i>There</i>

1378
01:38:16.149 --> 01:38:19.903
<i>By</i>

1379
01:38:20.070 --> 01:38:22.572
<i>Yourself</i>

1380
01:38:22.823 --> 01:38:25.742
<i>Nobody else</i>

1381
01:38:25.909 --> 01:38:29.663
<i>Nobody else can go for you</i>

1382
01:38:29.913 --> 01:38:36.169
<i>You. whoa</i>

1383
01:38:38.421 --> 01:38:44.761
<i>Got</i>

1384
01:38:45.095 --> 01:38:49.182
<i>To go</i>

1385
01:38:49.516 --> 01:38:53.103
<i>There</i>

1386
01:38:55.772 --> 01:39:00.527
<i>By</i>

1387
