- I said I thought it was.

1423
01:41:36.433 --> 01:41:38.935
- No. you said...
- Or under the mattress.

1424
01:41:39.269 --> 01:41:40.937
Or maybe in my chifforobe.

1425
01:41:41.104 --> 01:41:43.857
Well. I'm sorry. honey.

1426
01:41:44.024 --> 01:41:45.358
We need that ring.

1427
01:41:45.692 --> 01:41:48.111
It's at the bottom
of a durn big lake.

1428
